name: Frida Punk 092 - FRIxDIEGO
description:
Frida Kahlo X Diego Rivera
An Artist in love with another Artist.
So much in love they married twice. There was much Frida had to say about her love of Diego.

“I warn you that in this picture I am painting of Diego there will be colors which even I am not fully acquainted with. Besides, I love Diego so much I cannot be an objective speculator of him or his life.” - Frida Kahlo

💎 LIMITED EDITION PIECE CELEBRATING THE LOVE, LUST, ART AND LIFE OF FRIDA KAHLO & DIEGO RIVERA.
